Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的風找不到蹤迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.47,0:00:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取決于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天找出出人意料的凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的動機 意外的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.71,0:00:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似是小孩 頭腦卻異于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.60,0:01:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假裏 我們因爲旅行而去了長野的有森旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏 我們碰到了企業家城元英彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演員備前千鶴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.78,0:01:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第貳天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟蘭 有森先生還有阿忍三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.52,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到高原去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而城元先生跟宮部先生去釣魚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于擔心一整天都沒見到的千鶴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去她房間找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴小姐不是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被謀殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.31,0:02:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑天使的翅膀（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.69,0:02:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.82,0:02:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.76,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.79,0:02:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的星星真是太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都出神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.33,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美奈穗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我們馬上回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.81,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什魅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴小姐死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把巴士留在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們立刻回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.85,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是演員備前千鶴 30歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.19,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和丈夫城元英彥住在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡推定時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡推定時間是下午一點半到兩點半之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是窒息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現屍體時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個保險扣是拴上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.48,0:03:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要把門撞開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全部的窗戶都是反鎖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是備前千鶴是個有名的演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什魅令她自殺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 昨晚有突發事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突發事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她簽約的電影公司的負責人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說贊助商要求換人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.15,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子 妳不能進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個淘氣鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳東張西朢的幹什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏好像有些奇怪的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏有什麽奇怪的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏確實有痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.17,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是有人想把這裏變成一個密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這是怎麽回事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有人在裏面把窗戶上了鎖以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了制造一間密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把保險扣從牆上取了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後到走廊 把保險扣扣上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從外面把保險扣裝好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.06,0:05:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是從外面擰螺絲太難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就留下了這樣的擦痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把保險扣除下容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要裝上去就困難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.84,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴小姐就是用這個作墊子的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 哎喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.35,0:05:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙別人的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 人的腳趾應該是有指紋的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.89,0:05:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳問這麽多幹嘛 別多管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說千鶴小姐是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問這個台子上有沒有千鶴小姐的腳趾指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 這麽說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人把千鶴小姐吊起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說是他殺而不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚千鶴小姐去餐廳見誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟上去看清楚就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麽線索呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是些白色的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這裏也太熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.43,0:06:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道發現屍體的時候已經停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凶手特意關掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于備前千鶴小姐死的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一些問題要問妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 城元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像跟千鶴小姐正在辦離婚手續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在只剩下了贍養費的問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個是宮部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳要跟千鶴小姐解約是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這可不是我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因爲贊助商要換人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我要問問大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴小姐死亡的時間大約是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午一點半到兩點半之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家告訴我 妳們那時候在幹什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.69,0:07:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽意思 好像在調查不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道千鶴小姐是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現場情況來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他殺的可能性很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麽會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.14,0:07:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說宮部先生和城元先生釣魚去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上拾點從旅館出發 下午肆點回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在湖上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那個 我忘了帶便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拾貳點回來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅館的大廳裏跟毛利先生一起吃了飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點半又離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.49,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候妳有沒有看到千鶴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來之後就馬上去看她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我敲門卻沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就又回大廳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城元先生回來時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮部先生不就是一個人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一直在那裏吃午飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生跟阿忍小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.92,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和小蘭還有柯南去高原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元先生他們走後不久我們也出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達高原的時間大約是拾一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就一直待在高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約陸點我們才下山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到旅館的時間大約是柒點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有森先生一個人留在山上了 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因爲巴士的引擎壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去接他了 對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他在高原嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.38,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去了 絕對沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈穗小姐和穗奈美小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上我們剛要打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看見城元先生回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟毛利先生一起吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們送茶時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去過大廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點半左右我們送走了城元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.21,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆點之前 我們就和毛利先生一起看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲大家准備晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到大家回來 一直在廚房裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃時 千鶴小姐的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲她不讓我們打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們並沒有接近那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 妳一直在旅館吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一直在大廳裏看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了拾貳點半城元先生說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去看看而上過樓之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直沒見過任何人上樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說凶手是從緊急出口上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急出口的情況怎麽樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急出口在走廊的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從裏面可以隨意出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在外面沒有鑰匙就進不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽凶手就是旅館裏的人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.09,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因爲鑰匙在我這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很清楚了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠這樣做的人只有她們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麽也沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點半到肆點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們一直都在和我看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凶手就是妳們三個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.48,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反  反正沒有鑰匙的我不是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見得 即使沒有鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有辦法從緊急出口進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見得 即使沒有鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有辦法從緊急出口進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如城元先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拾貳點半妳去看千鶴小姐時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能從裏面打開緊急出口的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.77,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後放上一些障礙物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓門不能關上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在一點半以去湖邊爲借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從緊急出口回到旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害了千鶴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麽可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有這種可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮部先生 妳也可能成爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元先生的幫凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麽 警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可能跟城元先生一起回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又藏了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再利用城元先生打開的緊急出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入旅館殺了千鶴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳簡直把他們當成犯人了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個又怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鑰匙的只有妳們兩個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們下山不就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要亂說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從高原或湖邊回到旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要經過森林裏的一座橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才已經問過森林裏的工人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回旅館的只有城元先生的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有犯罪可能的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元 宮部 美奈穗 穗奈美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和毛利先生妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽 我也是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水戶警官說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定另有隱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.56,0:12:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如關掉的空調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在千鶴小姐身上的白色粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是一條飛翔的跑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.09,0:12:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護欄弄花了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔讓妳去檢查一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城元 宮部 美奈穗 穗奈美 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我妳們一整天的具體活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我是誰嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生妳怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是沈睡的小伍郎推理秀的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 這就是傳聞中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的事情就包在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳已經知道凶手是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.14,0:13:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道凶手是誰以及凶手所用的手法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手是用翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把不可能變成可能的魔法的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.43,0:13:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手就是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森光行先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳說什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小蘭他們一直都在高原上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.21,0:14:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有森先生不可能是凶手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說有森先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有魔法的翅膀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的翅膀到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是魔法的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在儲物室裏發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是滑翔翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.51,0:14:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我發現在被害者的頸部有在屋頂陽台擦過的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生利用滑翔翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從高原飛回旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後從屋頂上面爬到千鶴小姐的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再利用滑翔翼返回高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開大家去拿便當只有肆 伍分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而來回這裏至少要拾伍分鍾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且從旅館再飛回山上的高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不太可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 大家說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.43,0:15:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要殺害千鶴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.73,0:15:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要肆 伍分鍾就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前倘待在千鶴小姐身邊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴她一直留在旅館裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還有巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.28,0:15:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出發時有森先生跟阿忍說他去鎖門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另開一輛車和大家會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就到千鶴的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用高壓電槍什麽的把她弄昏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.35,0:16:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把她和滑翔翼都裝上巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水戶警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場勘查的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到那個空調沒開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴小姐白天不在房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後大約兩點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.71,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生在爲大家拿便當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.61,0:16:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴士內將千鶴小姐勒死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後以巴士引擎壞了爲由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人留在了高原上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後他打開滑翔翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上千鶴小姐的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從山上飛回了旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于旅館屋頂的燈全亮著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易就可以確定目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳降落在屋頂上以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就爬下陽台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.98,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從窗戶進入屋內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把屍體吊了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.88,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再用我剛才說的方法關上門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從緊急出口離開了旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.19,0:17:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我又是怎樣回到高原的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小蘭到達高原的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的確在那裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他是開巴士嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會被森林裏的工人看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.64,0:17:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果使用滑翔翼飛回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很難再用它飛回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.08,0:17:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說他用魔法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了任何人都不知道的魔法回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知道妳在說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的道具是妳的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生打手機叫阿忍小姐去接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就藏在車子的後備箱裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.53,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿忍小姐和蘭不知不覺間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和有森先生一起回到了高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子到達高原時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.21,0:18:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到阿忍小姐和蘭離開車子後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就鑽出後備箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.01,0:18:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像一直在那裏等著一樣 出現在妳們兩人面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有森先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是妳的推測而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.66,0:18:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.27,0:18:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他們來電話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在千鶴小姐裙子上的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山上稀有蝴蝶的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如妳們所聽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直留在旅館的千鶴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子上又怎麽會有山上蝴蝶的粉末呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.69,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽蘭說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高原時 有只蝴蝶曾飛到妳的肩膀上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知什麽原因死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就把粉末留在妳身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妳背千鶴小姐的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉末就沾到裙子上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽要把千鶴小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲弟弟報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.78,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.95,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟輝彥在東京讀大學時碰到了千鶴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝彥對美麗的千鶴越來越迷戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對千鶴來說 她只是玩玩而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.83,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一開始她把弟弟當成有錢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她交往 用了很多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴被名導演發掘後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越出名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終于跟輝彥分手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝彥爲了挽回千鶴的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了不少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.95,0:19:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至把爸爸的遺産 也就是這家旅館給抵押了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在這家旅館…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.23,0:19:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這家旅館已經是別人的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的經營者另有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳弟弟怎麽樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝彥他自暴自棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.84,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後和滑翔翼一起墜落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟追逐千鶴小姐 就跟追逐太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻因爲太熱而折斷了翅膀的天使一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 千鶴她知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我昨晚叫她到餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.73,0:20:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想讓她對弟弟道歉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那照片一點印象也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.34,0:20:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妳前男友有森輝彥的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟在跟妳分手之後就自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.21,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自殺關我什魅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他自己喜歡上我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不是要責備妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.13,0:21:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是唏朢妳在他墳前道個歉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自作主張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麽也不會做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟我一點關系都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.00,0:21:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就決定要殺她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以爲妳弟弟會高興嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.95,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶的死雖然是偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.45,0:21:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻認爲是妳弟弟的靈魂爲了阻止妳犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.29,0:21:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作蝴蝶而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也太慢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底到哪裏去了 真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.23,0:23:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.14,0:23:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.55,0:23:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是天使嗎 怎麽說也不像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被卡車撞倒的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.16,0:23:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地對逃跑的犯人叫著謎一樣的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.93,0:23:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被命名爲愁思郎事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.66,0:23:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時警察還展開了大規模的搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.53,0:24:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是因爲掌握核心事件的警官已經過世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查就停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.84,0:24:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前已經過了追訴時效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.61,0:24:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.11,0:24:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本廳刑事戀愛物語3（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.42,0:24:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.92,0:24:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站指示牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.92,0:24:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集的舞台是警視廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.29,0:24:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官和佐藤警官怎麽樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.59,0:24:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
