Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.53,0:01:06.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}爲了不再迷惑 請別松開妳的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(30,40)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}即使是互相傷害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.91,0:01:21.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我只是一直在迷惘的時空中找尋答案
