Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.54,0:22:17.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那次以後 不知多少個季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.49,0:22:23.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是笑著守候在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.86,Default5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,260)}{\fad(300,550)}寬帶協助\N\NZaRKz\N\NLXM3149\N\N小鳴\N\N自§基拉§由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.86,Default5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,200)}{\fad(300,550)}抄稿\N\N何強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.13,0:22:41.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不敢告訴我的事情 還有一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.64,0:22:46.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secret of my heart 並不是懷疑妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.55,0:22:52.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管何時 只要還有少許未來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.19,0:22:53.23,Default5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,200)}{\fad(300,550)}RMVB協助\N\Ntokibobo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.19,0:22:53.23,Default5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,200)}{\fad(300,550)}RMVB協助\N\NMagicYY
